            "stanza_text": "Fumerai-je au soir de ma vie\nUne pipe en bois de laurier ?\nNous voilà vieux, ma pauvre amie,\nJ'ai eu vingt ans en février."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Nous avons vu bien des feuillages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Des lacs, des golfes, la clarté",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Du songe, et de tous nos voyages,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Hélas ! qu'avons-nous rapporté ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Nous avons vu bien des feuillages,\nDes lacs, des golfes, la clarté\nDu songe, et de tous nos voyages,\nHélas ! qu'avons-nous rapporté ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Et tout cela n'est pas peu triste,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Mais dans l'ombre où nous nous plaignons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Enfin l'ironie oculiste",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Ouvre boutique de lorgnons.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et tout cela n'est pas peu triste,\nMais dans l'ombre où nous nous plaignons.\nEnfin l'ironie oculiste\nOuvre boutique de lorgnons."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Des lièvres dansent aux pelouses,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Et dans ma chambre mon espoir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Maintenant j'attends que tu couses",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Une rose à ton jupon noir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Des lièvres dansent aux pelouses,\nEt dans ma chambre mon espoir.\nMaintenant j'attends que tu couses\nUne rose à ton jupon noir."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Et que le rire ensevelisse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Sous des guirlandes de clarté,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Notre rêve, ce vieil Ulysse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Que les sirènes ont tenté.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et que le rire ensevelisse,\nSous des guirlandes de clarté,\nNotre rêve, ce vieil Ulysse\nQue les sirènes ont tenté."
        }
